data.description: Welcome Home! 3 bedroom 1 full bath home in move in ready condition. Property located in West Elsdon neighborhood, minutes walking distance to schools, shopping, restaurants, public transit, I55 and Midway Airport. Property features many recent upgrades, Large Mudroom in entrance, Updated flooring throughout, in unit washer/dryer. Kitchen with oven/range, dishwasher, all stainless steel appliances and butcher block counter tops! New ceramic tile in the bathroom. Ample storage space, Updated windows. There is a Huge driveway in the front of the property for plenty of parking. Seller willing to offer 2% Closing Cost Credit or for a Rate Buy Down.
